:: Mirror [Place bg-bedroom]
<h1 class="ptitle">BEDROOM</h1>
<br /><br />
<<link 'Change name'>>
	<<dialog 'Change name'>>	
		<<textbox "_mcName" `$player.name ?? ''`>>
		<<link 'OK'>>
			<<set $player.name = _mcName>>
			<<dialogclose>>	
			<<goto 'Mirror'>>
		<</link>>
	<</dialog>>	
<</link>>
<<link 'Leave'>>
    <<addmins 5>>
    <<goto 'Bedroom'>>
<</link>>